		%^BOLD%^Sundering Shadows Welcomes You!%^RESET%^

  Dear player,

    Welcome to the realms of Sundering Shadows. We appreciate the fact that you have desided to play this MUD. In our opinion, it is one of the best D&D muds around. We try to keep as faithful to the manuals as possible to ensure 100% playing pleasure.

   If you have questions, you can post them on the available boards or ask anyone online over the newbie, ooc, or wiz lines. Between players and immortals, you will generally find a quick response.

   We have many areas open and have several quests for you to solve, as well as countless other challenges.

   With the sincerest gratitude and appreciation, all of us here thank you for joining us.

		%^YELLOW%^HAVE FUN%^RESET%^
